    "This capability allows for adaptation to shallow-soil-moisture prediction tasks with significant variations.",
    "Figure 9g shows the training epochs required for each model, while Fig. 9h illustrates the time taken for 100 epochs.",
    "The 1D-CNN model demonstrates the fastest training speed and achieves early convergence.",
    "Conversely, LSTM shows slower training speed, which is attributed to its iterations.",
    "The Transformer trains quickly but converges at a slower pace than LSTM, resulting in a similar total training time."
